## Quick Reference

| Stage | Directory | Status Header | Next Action |
|-------|-----------|---------------|-------------|
| Writing | `drafted/` | `Draft` | Review & evaluate |
| Reviewed | `evaluated/` | `Evaluated` | Approve or reject |
| Approved | `ready/` | `Ready` | Implement |
| Done | *deleted* | N/A | Changelog entry |
